    "waitTime": 0,
    "IdSpeaker": "NPC214",
    "cnSpeaker": "伊迪丝",
    "enSpeaker": "Edith Ross",
    "Location": "",
    "cnAction": "皱了皱眉，像听到了什么粗俗的词汇，用手帕掩了掩鼻子",
    "cnWords": "好像听过一次。",
    "enAction": "",
    "enWords": "",
